<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ArBank - Om oss</title>
  <style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap');

:root {
  --bg-dark: #020617;
  --accent: #3b82f6;
  --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  --text-dim: #94a3b8;
  --card-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
}

/* 1. GAP-KILLER & BACKGROUND */
html, body {
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 100vh;
  background-color: var(--bg-dark);
  background-image: 
    radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, hsla(225,39%,20%,1) 0, transparent 50%), 
    radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, hsla(260,49%,20%,1) 0, transparent 50%);
  color: #f8fafc;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
}

/* 2. DOCK-TO-TOP HEADER */
header {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 80px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 8%;
  background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.85);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  z-index: 1000;
}

#logo {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}

nav a {
  margin-left: 30px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  transition: 0.3s;
}

nav a:hover { color: #fff; }

/* 3. CONTENT AREA */
main {
  flex-grow: 1;
  padding: 140px 20px 60px; /* Offset for header */
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

/* 4. THE INFO BOX (MATCHES THE CARDS) */
.info-section {
  background: var(--card-gradient);
  max-width: 700px;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 50px;
  border-radius: 28px;
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 30px;
}

.info-section h2 {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffffff, #94a3b8);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
}

.info-section p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: var(--text-dim);
}

.contact-item {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #fff;
}

.contact-item span {
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-right: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* 5. BACK BUTTON */
.btn-back {
  align-self: flex-start;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 14px 30px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: var(--glass);
  color: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  font-weight: 700;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.btn-back:hover {
  background: #fff;
  color: var(--bg-dark);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* 6. FOOTER */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px;
  background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.5);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
}

/* MOBILE FIX */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  header { height: auto; padding: 20px; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
  nav a { margin: 0 10px; }
  main { padding-top: 180px; }
  .info-section { padding: 30px; }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <a href="/" id="logo">ArBank</a>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Hjem</a>
      <a href="/konto">Konto</a>
      <a href="/konto/tjenester">Tjenester</a>
      <a href="/om-oss">Om Oss</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="info-section">
      <h2>Om ArBank</h2>
      <p>ArBank er en moderne bank som tilbyr sikre og raske digitale løsninger for våre kunder. Vi legger stor vekt på brukervennlighet, sikkerhet og personlig service.</p>

      <h2>Kontaktinformasjon</h2>
      <p class="contact-item"><span>Telefon:</span> +47 123 45 678 </p>
      <p class="contact-item"><span>Adresse:</span> Fyrstikkalleen 21, Oslo, Norge</p>

      <a href="/" class="btn-back">Tilbake til Hjem</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ArBank. Alle rettigheter reservert.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
